page.title: 15Government
page.content:
The study area is part of the electoral constituency of CORBY...and the present Member of Parliament is William Powell, representing the Conservative Party.... the elected Government. For County Council elections the district is part of the Oundle Electoral Division, and is served by its elected member Mr W.M.Clack. The area is also administered by East Northants Council,with Mr Glitheroe JP as the elected representative. Deene Parish Council is chaired by Mr E.Sansom.
There are 49 names on the Electoral Register for Deene, and 32 for Deenethorpe (10 October 1984).
